{"tid":1368163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"727民間救護車tg","createTime":"2019-07-26T12:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T16:46:38.000Z","uid":92107,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3afea066f2f43892db80ceb4674b234e1a711ad5","tid":1368163,"uid":92107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:12:51.000Z","msg":"民間救護車嘅救援用品比較少，主要現場止血，並且送傷者到安全嘅地方為主。有興趣嘅車主，可以車埋你隔離做救護嗰個，一齊出嚟。架車最好係啲錢七，唔驚俾人扑爛。如果車主自己識急救都可以，但係一心不能二用，請注意安全。<br />\n車入邊要有嘅物資，生理鹽水、繃帶、紗布、防水膠布或者膠貼（噴霧膠布都得）<br />\n歡迎車手加救護入grp報到<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/YLwhitecar727\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FYLwhitecar727&d=0Lcuuml91xlF79uKCzc07v7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=480be252\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/YLwhitecar727</a><br />\n<br />\n由於開grp倉猝，各位車手同救護，請留意收兵嗰邊嘅資訊，在自行聽日係我哋呢個grp入面自行分工走位<br />\n<br />\n車上會有基本急救用品洗傷口止血，並把傷者從危險環境帶走。<br />\n如果只係要而在服務，請去<a href=\"https://t.me/hkuber\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkuber&d=0Lcuuml91xlF79uKCzc07v7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=b9d15847\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkuber</a>"},{"pid":"77bac22b9ba42462b3943530f58ccb0bd83a8637","tid":1368163,"uid":107487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:13:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b891e76ef459bb801df469958d2c598b4b8ffc7f","tid":1368163,"uid":261986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:14:35.000Z","msg":"緊急727戰術，請幫推。<br />\n<br />\n727奇招： 智取元朗！道德抗暴！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1367929\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1367929</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"895abf63d7651fc6da4bb24f6eac9e9974534389","tid":1368163,"uid":107487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:15:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0f58f3d47d0cc